snippet: Milagro G. Canjura, 31, was discovered by Suffolk County police officers inside a parked car near her home in Bay Shore. No suspects have been identified.
abstract: Police officers responding to reports of gunfire in Bay Shore, LI, find body of pregnant woman Milagro G Canjura in parked car near her home; she had been shot several times; no suspects have been identified.
lead_paragraph: Milagro G. Canjura, 31, was discovered by Suffolk County police officers inside a parked car near her home in Bay Shore. No suspects have been identified.

headline.main: Pregnant Woman Is Killed in Shooting on Long Island
